text.tspan: Master: outb(0x21, 0x20) IRQ0 maps to vector 32
Slave: outb(0xA1, 0x28) IRQ8 maps to vector 40

div.p: io_wait() between writes: outb(0x80, 0x00) ~14s delay POST diagnostic port write. Required for 8259 state machine settling time on real hardware.
Spurious IRQ Detection: IRQ7 / IRQ15 may be spurious. Check ISR before sending EOI: outb(0x20, 0x0B) read ISR If bit not set: do NOT send EOI to that PIC (it never set ISR).

Default Collision (before remap): IRQ0 vec 8 = Double Fault handler IRQ1 vec 9 = Invalid TSS IRQ2 vec 10 = Segment Not Present IRQ3 vec 11 = Stack Fault IRQ4 vec 12 = General Protection IRQ5 vec 13 = GPF IRQ6 vec 14 = Page Fault IRQ7 vec 15 = Reserved
